<p>The Long form pattern is a flexible pattern that is designed to be repeated a large number of times on a page utilising a series of variations to give a consistent look and feel that works well for longer passages of text enriched with media like images, video and audio. It is a rather unique pattern in that there are also several sub-patterns that are made available inside this pattern.</p>

<h2>Usage</h2>

<ul>
	<li>Use a university header and university footer</li>
    <li>use as many long-form sections as you want in between</li>
    <li>Ensure that the final one has the watermark variant.</li>
</ul>

